Mine’s from Glossier, and we’re calling it Priming Moisturizer Balance, because it balances the look of oily skin over time. She’s a beaut, but more importantly, she works, and she's available now on Glossier.com!

node.text: Welcome to Glossier Seattle! ✨ Even as a digital-first company, we’ve always viewed our retail experiences as an essential part of bringing the world of Glossier to life with our community. For our first of many new locations, we looked to the forests of the Pacific Northwest and drew inspiration from mushrooms. 🍄 Fungi have so many incredible qualities, like a unique ability to grow and thrive in unlikely places—some even claim they have the power to revolutionize the way we live in the future. Well, the future is now: Glossier Seattle, a permanent store, opens at 1514 10th Ave TODAY (!!!). We’ll meet you there.

node.text: It’s finally happening! After 522 days (!), we are back with our first new permanent store. Glossier Seattle 🏔️ will open this Friday, August 20th at 11AM, at 1514 10th Ave. Stop by to shop, explore the new space, or just say 👋. We’re *so* happy to be back and can’t wait to see you in four days. Let the countdown begin.
